  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\n```\r\ntruffle(rinkeby)> Error: PollingBlockTracker - encountered an error while attempting to update latest block:\r\nError: Client network socket disconnected before secure TLS connection was established\r\n    at connResetException (node:internal/errors:631:14)\r\n    at TLSSocket.onConnectEnd (node:_tls_wrap:1565:19)\r\n    at TLSSocket.emit (node:events:388:22)\r\n    at TLSSocket.EventEmitter.emit (node:domain:470:12)\r\n    at endReadableNT (node:internal/streams/readable:1305:12)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:80:21)\r\n    at PollingBlockTracker._performSync (D:\\smartcontracts\\crowdsales-experiments\\node_modules\\eth-block-tracker\\src\\polling.js:51:24)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:93:5)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1.  Initiated truffle env with default settings\r\n2. Updated network and added rinkeby network to truffle-config\r\n```\r\n      rinkeby: {\r\n          provider: () => new HDWalletProvider(\r\n              mnemonic, `https://eth-rinkeby.alchemyapi.io/v2/${alchemyApiKey}`\r\n          ),\r\n          network_id: 4,\r\n          gasPrice: 10e9,\r\n          skipDryRun: true\r\n      }\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n3. Run this\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n npx truffle console --network rinkeby\r\n```\r\n\r\n4. It works for some time but fails randomly\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Windows 10\r\n* Truffle v5.1.57 (core: 5.1.57)\r\n* Solidity - 0.7.5 (solc-js)\r\n* Node v15.5.0\r\n* Web3.js v1.2.9\r\n",
